---
title: Roast Butternut Pumpkin & Feta Salad with Creamy Pesto & Garlic-Herb Croutons
description: The best salads are a combination of flavours, textures and colours – and with golden roasted pumpkin, herby croutons, earthy beetroot and creamy feta, this one ticks all the boxes.
